### Checkout Payments API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4080/api/v1
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Variables
@checkoutOrderId = 1
@paymentId = 1

### 1. Initiate Payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkout-payments/initiate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checkout_order_id": {{checkoutOrderId}},
  "payment_method_code": "gcash",
  "payment_type": "full"
}

### 2. Get Payment Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/checkout-payments/{{paymentId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get Payment Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/checkout-payments/{{paymentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. List Payments
GET {{baseUrl}}/checkout-payments?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. List Payments by Order
GET {{baseUrl}}/checkout-payments?checkout_order_id={{checkoutOrderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Process Refund
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkout-payments/{{paymentId}}/refund
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "reason": "Customer requested refund"
}

### 7. Webhook (PayMongo Callback)
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkout-payments/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gateway_transaction_id": "pay_abc123xyz",
  "gateway_reference_number": "REF123456",
  "gateway_response": {
    "type": "payment.paid",
    "data": {
      "id": "pay_abc123xyz",
      "attributes": {
        "status": "paid",
        "amount": 5000,
        "paid_at": "2024-12-11T10:00:00Z"
      }
    }
  }
}



